維季姆境內設有{{le|維季姆機場|Vitim Airport}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Vitim Airport|url=http://www.ourairports.com/airports/UERT/|publisher=OurAirports|accessdate=2013-01-23|archive-date=2012-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120224125133/http://www.ourairports.com/airports/UERT/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

